>>  parse value d with f1 '|' f2 '|' f3 '|' f4
>>
>>or...
>>
>>  parse var d f1 '|' f2 '|' f3 '|' f4

A better, more general solution is

 do while d <> ""
  parse var d field '|' d
  call process_it d
 end

or

 array. = ""
 do i = 1 while d <> ""
  parse var d array.i '|' d
 end

 - seb


